snippet.title: ROCKY Pennington WITNESS Statement - Johnny Depp v Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Amber Heard's friend Rocky Pennigton provided this witness statement against Johnny Depp in the UK trial stating over and again that Amber Heard told her what happened but she didn't see Johnny Depp actually do anything.

Johnny Depp will have justice soon enough.
